        <td colspan="3" style="width:133px;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The Maximum Contact Shear Stress,Ʈ<text style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;">max</text>, is at a depth below the Cam and Roller Surfaces at about Z = 0.786×b. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">You should make sure that the of case hardness depth is a minimum of 1.41×b, even better to make sure it is 2×b</para>
        </td>
